{"tid":881691,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"養狗一定要用狗帶","createTime":"2018-10-29T15:38:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T02:03:49.000Z","uid":157509,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"984cbe55043304f9bef755651f9db8e371472801","tid":881691,"uid":157509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T15:38:18.000Z","msg":"頭先係獸醫診所<br />\n有個男人抱住隻狗衝入黎<br />\n話隻狗比車撞親叫醫生救佢<br />\n果時隻狗仔已經無反應<br />\n之後聽到因爲無用狗帶<br />\n個男人喊哂咁好自責<br />\n<br />\n其實叫養狗既人用狗帶 就好似叫養貓既人裝窗網咁<br />\n好似係常識<br />\n但永遠有班人話由細到大無用都無事<br />\n好老土咁講無事係你好彩<br />\n當出事既時候先識後悔<br />\n<br />\nRIP 狗仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf9493c76e4678b76f3d6075be7da39239d91a9","tid":881691,"uid":158613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T15:43:13.000Z","msg":"害死自己隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88665f13b3e1fa8301ce116489a64e0bc7af9531","tid":881691,"uid":43530,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T15:47:45.000Z","msg":"啲人懶鳩勁咁以為自己馴獸師<br />\n隻狗會聽佢支笛<br />\n屌，講真隻狗happy起上黎理鳩你，狗衝先算<br />\n咁咪出事囉"},{"pid":"48345e385fb6c183b6efb21cc92c7d9e993ae2c5","tid":881691,"uid":157509,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"aaf9493c76e4678b76f3d6075be7da39239d91a9","tid":881691,"uid":158613,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T15:43:13.000Z","msg":"害死自己隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T16:07:45.000Z","msg":"呢d人永遠都話由細到大隻狗行路都痴實我<br />\n唔洗用狗帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bafa47d410235bb532d775d8baa93a89d4427905","tid":881691,"uid":54901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T02:02:48.000Z","msg":"啲人鍾意懶型，覺得隻狗識跟住自己行東行西好威囉 <br />\n但唔諗下香港地人多車多 對面黎緊乜嘢無人估到 <br />\n如果個仔得兩三歲都唔會唔拖住手喇 狗仔咪又係得兩三歲小朋友嘅思想咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c394d4a3e4fb641482631fd2417f97b52f346ff6","tid":881691,"uid":54901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T02:03:49.000Z","msg":"呢啲統一稱為殺狗兇手"}]}